(74, 21, NULL, 'assistant', 'That\'s a great question to check your pipeline, Iconic Leader!\n\nI can see your general account information, but I don\'t have the precise, up-to-the-minute list of your active clients or hot leads right now. That data is securely held within the CRM section of the RealtorOne app.\n\nYour next best step is to **open the RealtorOne app and navigate to the \'CRM\' tab** to view your current client list.\n\nAre you looking to check on a specific type of lead, like hot leads or active pipeline status?', '2026-04-25 13:13:00', '2026-04-25 13:13:00', 414, 115, 529, 'google/gemini-2.5-flash-lite-preview-09-2025'),
